# Update FEATURES.md with new features

When you add or change **user-facing or significant technical features** in this project:

1. **Update [FEATURES.md](FEATURES.md)** in the same change set:
   - Add the feature under the appropriate section (or add a new section if needed).
   - Keep descriptions concise and consistent with the existing style.
   - If the feature is admin-only or mediator-only, say so.

2. **Optionally update [README.md](README.md)** if the new feature belongs in the high-level feature list there.

Do not leave FEATURES.md outdated after implementing a new feature.
